
ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_InitialLeftEdge: ( ti_Tag = $80080003 )

Specify in ti_Data the initial 
horizontal position of the requester.


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_InitialTopEdge: ( ti_Tag = $80080004 )

Specify in ti_Data the initial 
vertical position of the requester.


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_InitialWidth: ( ti_Tag = $80080005 )

Specify in ti_Data the initial width 
of the requester.


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_InitialHeight: ( ti_Tag = $80080006 )

Specify in ti_Data the initial height
of the requester.


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_InitialName: ( ti_Tag = $8008000A )

Specify in ti_Data a pointer to a null
terminated string which is to be the
default contents of the Name gadget.


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_InitialSize: ( ti_Tag = $8008000B )

Specify in ti_Data the default Size
in the font requester.


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_InitialStyle: ( ti_Tag = $8008000C )

Specify in ti_Data the default Style
for the font requester.

Style flags can be found in "graphics/text.h"


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_InitialFlags: ( ti_Tag = $8008000D )

Specify in ti_Data the default font Flags
for the font requester.

Font flags can be found in "graphics/text.h"


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_InitialFrontPen: ( ti_Tag = $8008000E )

Specify in ti_Data the default front pen
in the font requester.


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_InitialBackPen: ( ti_Tag = $8008000F )

Specify in ti_Data the default back pen
in the font requester.


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_InitialDrawMode: ( ti_Tag = $8008003B )

Specify in ti_Data the ordinal number
(in the cycle gadget) of the default
selected DrawMode in the font requester.


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_FixedWidthOnly: ( ti_Tag = $80080030 )

Specify in ti_Data a True boolean to
limit the available fonts in the requester
to fixed width only.


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_MinHeight: ( ti_Tag = $80080010 )

Specify in ti_Data the Minimum height of
font that the requester is to include.


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_MaxHeight: ( ti_Tag = $80080010 )

Specify in ti_Data the Maximum height of
font that the requester is to include.


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_FilterFunc: ( ti_Tag = $80080031 )

Specify a pointer to a custom Hook function 
to be used for filtering fonts.
(See the RKM's for more details).


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_HookFunc: ( ti_Tag = $80080007 )

Specify a pointer to a custom function
as a combined callback function.
(See the RKM's for more details).


ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_ModeList: ( ti_Tag = $80080015 )

Specify a pointer in ti_Data, to a 
Null-pointer terminated array of strings
to be used as the DrawMode Cycle Gadget.
The first string replaces the Label, the
rest replace the elements of the gadget.

